+"""
+Seed the default LifeLens community spheres with demo activity.
+
+This uses firebase-admin because Firestore security rules correctly prevent the
+Flutter client from impersonating other users. It is safe to rerun: sphere,
+member, post, and reaction documents use deterministic IDs and are upserted.
+
+Auth options:
+- FIREBASE_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON='{"type":"service_account", ...}'
+- GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/path/to/service-account.json
+- Application Default Credentials
